casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Brockmeier.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Brockmeier (1990), 51 Ohio St. 3d 603.]

(No. 90-745 Submitted May 8, 1990 Decided May 16, 1990.)

The resignation of Frederick Brockmeier IV as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
